fi.tuni.tamk

Class Resources

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.tuni.tamk.Resources

  • public class Resources
extends java.lang.Object
    Resources class is used to initialize all the Textures, Musics, Fonts and Sounds only once to avoid memory build-ups. The class has also a method for changing the Box Textures according to the language.
